def process_single_run(workflow, comfy_env_path, timeout_seconds,
                      prompt_text, filename_prefix, run_type, idx):
    """
    å•æ¬¡å¤„ç†è¿è¡Œ
    
    Returns:
        bool: å¤„ç†æ˜¯å¦æˆåŠŸ
    """
    # å¤åˆ¶å·¥ä½œæµ
    modified_workflow = json.loads(json.dumps(workflow))
    
    # æ›´æ–°æç¤ºæ–‡æœ¬åˆ°èŠ‚ç‚¹113çš„valueè¾“å…¥
    modified_workflow["113"]["inputs"]["value"] = prompt_text
    
    # æ›´æ–°è¾“å‡ºæ–‡ä»¶åå‰ç¼€
    if "107" in modified_workflow:
        modified_workflow["107"]["inputs"]["filename_prefix"] = filename_prefix
    
    # å…³é”®ä¿®å¤ï¼šåœ¨tryå—å¤–åˆå§‹åŒ–å˜é‡
    temp_workflow_path = None
    
    try:
        # åˆ›å»ºä¸´æ—¶å·¥ä½œæµæ–‡ä»¶
        with tempfile.NamedTemporaryFile(mode='w', suffix='æ.json', delete=False, encoding='utf-8') as temp_file:
            json.dump(modified_workflow, temp_file, indent=2)
            temp_workflow_path = temp_file.name
        
        # æ„å»ºå‘½ä»¤
        cmd = [comfy_env_path, "run", "--workflow", temp_workflow_path, "--wait", "--timeout", str(timeout_seconds)]
        
        print(f"   ğŸ¯ è¿è¡Œç±»å‹: {run_type}")
        print(f"   ğŸ“ æç¤ºæ–‡æœ¬: {prompt_text[:100]}...")
        print(f"   ğŸ’¾ è¾“å‡ºå‰ç¼€: {filename_prefix}")
        print(f"   âš¡ æ‰§è¡Œå‘½ä»¤: {' '.join(cmd)}")
        
        # æ‰§è¡Œå‘½ä»¤å¹¶æ•è·è¾“å‡º
        result = subprocess.run(
            cmd, 
            capture_output=True, 
            text=True, 
            timeout=timeout_seconds + 30
        )
        
        # æ ¼å¼åŒ–è¾“å‡ºç»“æœ
        print(f"   ğŸ“‹ è¿”å›ç : {result.returncode}")
        
        if result.stdout:
            stdout_lines = [line for line in result.stdout.strip().split('\n') if line.strip()]
            if stdout_lines:
                print(f"   æ ‡å‡†è¾“å‡º: {stdout_lines[-1][:100]}...")
        
        if result.stderr:
            stderr_lines = [line for line in result.stderr.strip().split('\n') if line.strip()]
            if stderr_lines:
                print(f"   é”™è¯¯è¾“å‡º: {stderr_lines[-1][:100]}...")
        
        success = result.returncode == 0
        status_icon = "âœ…" if success else "âŒ"
        print(f"   {status_icon} å¤„ç†{'æˆåŠŸ' if success else 'å¤±è´¥'}")
        
        return success
            
    except subprocess.TimeoutExpired:
        print("   â° å¤„ç†è¶…æ—¶")
        return False
    except Exception as e:
        print(f"   ğŸ’¥ å¼‚å¸¸: {str(e)}")
        return False
    finally:
        # å…³é”®ä¿®å¤ï¼šå®‰å…¨åœ°æ¸…ç†ä¸´æ—¶æ–‡ä»¶
        if temp_workflow_path is not None and os.path.exists(temp_workflow_path):
            try:

                print(f"   ğŸ—‘ï¸  å·²æ¸…ç†ä¸´æ—¶å·¥ä½œæµæ–‡ä»¶: {os.path.basename(temp_workflow_path)}")
            except Exception as e:
                print(f"   âš ï¸  æ¸…ç†ä¸´æ—¶æ–‡ä»¶æ—¶å‡ºé”™: {str(e)}")


def main():

            comfy_env_path=args.comfy_env,
            timeout_seconds=args.timeout,
            output_dir=args.output_dir,
            input_dir=args.input_dir,

        )
        
        print("ğŸ‰ æ‰€æœ‰ä½“è‚²ç”·å­©æç¤ºæ–‡æœ¬è§†é¢‘ç”Ÿæˆå¤„ç†å®Œæˆï¼")

æ    return 0
